        <li><a href="/learn/guides/geo/" class="text-sm text-text-light-muted hover:text-accent-bright transition-colors">GEO Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/learn/guides/complete-guide-ai-search/" class="text-sm text-text-light-muted hover:text-accent-bright transition-colors">Complete Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/learn/tools/llms-txt-generator/" class="text-sm text-text-light-muted hover:text-accent-bright transition-colors">Free llms.txt Generator</a></li>
